text: The Most Esteemed Family Order of Seri Utama () is an order of Brunei. It was established on 1 March 1954 by Sultan Omar Ali Saifuddien III. The order carries the post-nominal letters "DK" as well as the title "Dato Seri Utama". == See also == * Family Order of Laila Utama == References == Category:Orders, decorations, and medals of Brunei Category:Awards established in 1954 Category:1954 establishments in Brunei
title: Family Order of Seri Utama
